transcript:

Executive: Mere PC PC ko webcam nahi hai.
Executive: To koi dikkat aayega?
Customer: No issue. If you click directly on the video meet link I have shared, you will join directly. There will be no issue.
Executive: Okay. Okay.
Executive: Okay. Theek hai. Join in 5 minutes. As soon as this video meet ends, I will join.
Customer: Okay.
Executive: Okay.
